        "content": "### Read Pending Queue (Notion)\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Keep Valid Bookings · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token",
